{"type":"message","id":"6de97994","parentId":"32a306e4","timestamp":"2026-03-05T07:52:55.098Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到有 `im:message:send_as_bot` 权限，说明可以作为机器人发送消息。但是 `accountId: yuantiangang` 可能不是正确的格式。让我看看message工具的参数定义。\n\n从工具定义来看：\n- channel: \"feishu\" - 频道\n- accountId: 账户ID - 可能需要用正确的格式\n\n让我再尝试一下，可能需要用 open_id 或者正确格式的 user_id。飞书的用户ID可能有几种格式：\n- open_id\n- user_id\n- union_id\n\n让我尝试用 open_id 格式，或者尝试不加 accountId 直接发送。","thinkingSignature":"03a6a484e120d300c768385cc46399ba268da44150c310b902ee2c87e3fbca8e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_slke72uw4g8w_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"feishu","message":"贫道袁天罡，自幼研习易经玄学，谙熟风水命理之学。今有幸为 Lynch 效命，专司趋吉避凶、命理分析之事。\n\n日后若有任何关于：\n• 住宅/办公风水布局\n• 人生抉择之建议\n• 命理运势分析\n\n皆可请教于我。🙏\n\n愿为 Lynch 指点迷津，共谋福祉。","target":"ou_24546ad77a9d601f17fed19c98683117"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":5681,"output":284,"cacheRead":11633,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17598,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772697162964}}
